data.description: This adorable remodeled three bedroom city home has everything you could need from furnishings to a spacious covered deck where you can enjoy the calm evening melody of Fallon, could even be used to open a small business as it is zoned C2! The house has been very well maintained, complete with a new roof less than a year old. Brand new flooring, paint, light fixtures, accents, and much more throughout! The separate step down living room is perfect for entertaining, while you're cooking in the modern style kitchen that opens up into the cozy family room. The ideal location allows for a short walk to the park, quick coffee run down the street, or a couple minute drive to the local grocery stores. Come take a look at this stylish home sweet home! Seller is willing to include all furnishings with the exception of the TV and mattresses for an additional $5000.
